<pre><code>Has anyone managed to rewrite this rule for lighttpd?

Lighttpd uses the PCRE engine.

RewriteRule !\.(js|ico|gif|jpg|png|css)$ index.php

Syntax looks like this:

url.rewrite-once = ( "&lt;regex&gt;" =&gt; "&lt;relative-uri&gt;" )
</code></pre>

